<br>
Calm down.<br>
<br>
I'm not trying to shrug off the tragedy. I'm putting it into perspective. I'm not putting the blinkers on. This day I tried to remember every innocent life taken....not just those taken on 9/11.<br>
<br>
I'm not here to tell you that you shouldn't remember the victims of 9/11. You should. I'm here to tell you that this is not the first or last time innocent people have died.<br>
<br>
Remember them all.<br>
